'''圣路加堂'''（St Luke's Church, Liverpool）是一座已废弃的[[圣公会|圣公会]]教堂，位于英国[[利物浦|利物浦]]贝里街。

该堂建于1811-1832年，由约翰·福斯特父子设计。该堂在1941年德军空袭时严重受损，仅存无屋顶的外壳，现在作为战争死者纪念馆，以及展览以及戏剧、诗歌、舞蹈等文化活动场地<ref>{{Citation| url = http://www.usl.org.uk/content/LunchAtStLukes.aspx| title = Lunch at St Lukes| accessdate = 2013-04-09| publisher = Urban Strawberry Lunch| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130613152312/http://www.usl.org.uk/content/LunchAtStLukes.aspx| archivedate = 2013-06-13}}</ref><ref>{{Citation| url = http://www.liverpool.com/events-features/st.-luke-s...-cinema.html| title = St. Luke's... cinema?| accessdate = 2013-04-09| publisher = Trinity Mirror North West & North Wales| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100110035212/http://www.liverpool.com/events-features/st.-luke-s...-cinema.html| archive-date = 2010-01-10| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.visitliverpool.com/things-to-do/attractions/search/st-lukes-bombed-out-church-p327651| title = St Luke's (bombed out) Church| accessdate =2013-04-09| publisher = Liverpool City Region Local Enterprise Partnership}}</ref>。教堂、围墙、门均列为II*级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]。

